				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Mage pets belong to mages.
<br />
Mages get nukes.
<br />
Mages are therefore casters, and not melee.
<br />

<br />
It would be overpowering to give our pets the new melee combat system, and it would not be overpowering to give bst pets the new combat system, since beastlords are hybrids and not casters.
<br />

<br />
To reiterate: Casters are teh evil, overpowered, monsters according to melees. This combat system is to placate melees. Beastlords get away with a great deal, so why not this too? <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" />
